GeneralComments: http://www.ironhorservresort.com/   Catering to the comfort and convenience of our guests, the Iron Horse RV Resort is proud to offer all the amenities you could want in an rv resort. a convenience store, great room, rec room, laundry, dog park, children's play area and more are all on-site. Take advantage of full hook-ups for RVs, our free cable TV and wi-fi or enjoy one of our on-site cottages loaded with the comforts of home.   While you are staying at the Iron Horse RV Resort, take a break from the road and indulge yourself in Hilton® amenities: the pool, fitness room, Great American Grill, and more are waiting for you at our neighboring Hilton Garden Inn.                              Handy travel tip:  if you eat at the Hilton Garden Inn right up the hill from the RV park, and you mention you’re staying at the RV park, they’ll give you 20% off your meal.
